statements.sql:
select sch_service_bookings.id,
sch_service_bookings.status,
cmn_customers.full_name as customer,
cmn_customers.phone_no as customer_phone_no,
cmn_branches.name as branch,
sch_employees.full_name as employee,
sch_services.title as service,
sch_service_bookings.date,
sch_service_bookings.start_time,
sch_service_bookings.remarks,
sch_service_bookings.service_amount-sch_service_bookings.paid_amount as due from `sch_service_bookings` inner join `sch_services` on `sch_service_bookings`.`sch_service_id` = `sch_services`.`id` inner join `cmn_customers` on `sch_service_bookings`.`cmn_customer_id` = `cmn_customers`.`id` inner join `cmn_branches` on `sch_service_bookings`.`cmn_branch_id` = `cmn_branches`.`id` inner join `sch_employees` on `sch_service_bookings`.`sch_employee_id` = `sch_employees`.`id` where `sch_service_bookings`.`cmn_branch_id` in (1) and `sch_service_bookings`.`date` = '2023-11-09' and `sch_service_bookings`.`status` != 4 order by sch_service_bookings.date desc, start_time desc
